    public abstract class AbstractInterpreter<U>
extends android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.Void,android.util.Pair<U,ResponseListener<U>>,java.lang.Void>
implements Interpreter
    A reasonable skeletal implementation of much of the Interpreter interface.
